The usage of the hole between 1M and kernel stack:

 Offset     | Size      | Usage                 | Comments
============#===========#=======================#=========================================
 0x0        | 0x1000    | APIC                  | 
============#===========#=======================#=========================================
 0x1000     | 0x1000    | I/O APIC              |
============#===========#=======================#=========================================
 0x2000     | 0x2000    | HPET                  |
============#===========#=======================#=========================================